data.description: This delightful property offers an open and inviting floor-plan, where the heart of the home is a spacious kitchen that seamlessly flows into the cozy living room, creating the perfect space for gatherings and entertaining guests. Adjacent to the kitchen is a separate dining room. There's a 3-car tandem garage, providing plenty of space for your vehicles, equipment, and more. Upstairs, discover three generously sized bedrooms, each offering comfort and privacy for the whole family. Additionally, a versatile loft space awaits, ready to be transformed into a home office, play area, or anything your heart desires. The unfinished basement presents a blank canvas, allowing you the exciting opportunity to customize and complete it to your exact preferences, creating your own unique space. There is NO HOA!  Don't miss the chance to make this incredible house your home. With its spacious interior, fantastic garage, and endless possibilities, it's the perfect canvas to create your forever haven. Come and see the potential that awaits you.
